      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Sunday Feb 12,1956.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Springfield 9, Massachusetts.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Washington, D.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "I know that you are a very busy man but do you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "suppose that you could enlighten me on the following subject.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "My name is [REDACTED] and I am 15 years",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "of age and am a student at Technical High School here in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Springfield, Massachusetts.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Recently I became very interested in one of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "most amazing dramas of our time, the phenomena of the flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "saucers. In a book which I have just read, entitled \"flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "saucers uncensored\" written by Harold T. Wilkins, the author",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "tells of many cases and sightings of flying saucers which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "correspondents around the world have sent him.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "One story which he received from a correspondent in California,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "tells the story of two men who supposedly came from Venus and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "went to a Los Angeles journalist in March 1953. These men did",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "strange things which made someone so suspicious that he suppo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "sedly contacted the F.B.I., which is supposed to have sent an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "investigator to find out what was going on, but in some strange",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "way the Venusians by using telepathic power or some strange",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "faculty of prevision did not return to the office again. It was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "said that the F.B.I. was never able to find them for question-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "ing.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "I wonder if this story is true, and if you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "were really notified. I know of you were notified you couldn't",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "tell me anyting about the incident, but I am very curious.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Could you possibly tell me if you were noti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "fied and if the story is true.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "I would appreciate hearing from you.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Yours truly,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
